snippet.title: @CozyK Shares Her Most Anticipated Game of 2025 | Tales of the Shire at #thegameawards
snippet.description:
ICYMI @CozyK shared her love of cosy games and what she's looking forward to when Tales of the Shire comes out on March 25th, 2025.

From Wētā Workshop, known for their work in the film industry, comes Tales of the Shire: A The Lord of the Rings Game, a Hobbit life sim set in the Middle-earth universe of J.R.R. Tolkien.
